# Project Structure Reference

## Standard Web Environment Structure

```
{{ project_name }}/

  design/                          # Design documents
    spec.json                      # Project specification
    api_contracts.md               # API endpoint definitions
    components.md                  # UI component inventory

  app/
    frontend/                      # React + Vite application
      public/
        favicon.ico
      src/
        components/
          ui/                      # Basic UI: Button, Input, Card, Modal
          features/                # Business: specific to this app
        layouts/                   # MainLayout, Header, Sidebar, Footer
        pages/                     # Dashboard, Login, Settings, etc.
        hooks/                     # useAuth, useFetch, etc.
        services/                  # api.js, auth.js
        stores/                    # State: context or zustand
        styles/                    # index.css, theme.css
        utils/                     # helpers, formatters
        App.jsx
        main.jsx
      index.html
      package.json
      vite.config.js
      Dockerfile

    backend/                       # Express.js API
      src/
        config/                    # env.js, database.js, auth.js
        controllers/               # Request handlers
        middleware/                # auth, errorHandler, validation
        models/                    # Sequelize models
        routes/                    # index.js, auth.js, users.js
        services/                  # Business logic
        utils/                     # Helpers
        app.js                     # Express app setup
        server.js                  # Server entry point
      package.json
      Dockerfile

    database/                      # PostgreSQL
      init/
        01_schema.sql              # Table definitions
        02_seed.sql                # Initial data
      Dockerfile

  env/                             # OpenEnv Adapter
    models.py                      # WebAction, WebObservation, WebState
    client.py                      # WebEnvClient
    openenv.yaml                   # Environment configuration
    pyproject.toml
    server/
      environment.py               # Environment logic
      app.py                       # FastAPI app
      Dockerfile

  docker/
    docker-compose.yml             # Production config
    docker-compose.dev.yml         # Development config

  config.yaml                      # Project configuration
```

## Key Conventions

### Frontend
- Use JSX (not TSX) for components
- All layouts in `layouts/` - never create `layout/`, `Layout/`, or `components/layout/`
- Pages are route components in `pages/`
- Shared UI in `components/ui/`
- Feature-specific components in `components/features/`

### Backend
- CommonJS (require/module.exports) not ESM
- Routes mounted under `/api`
- Health check at `/health`
- Models use Sequelize
- Authentication via JWT

### Database
- PostgreSQL 15+
- Schema in numbered SQL files
- Seed data for development

### Docker
- Backend on port 5001
- Frontend on port 3000
- Database on port 5432

